node.text:
Winding down 🌅
Haven’t drawn a “dragon n chill” drawing in quite some time, it feels like. It’s well overdue XD
It’s also a small ode to the turntable/record player. There’s something peaceful about actively listening to vinyl. 
Process vid on third swipe, but for some reason IG decided to crop it around the edges a little ha

node.text:
Rainbowfish No.8

Wow, this one took a long time to complete, and went through a ton of changes lol. Have been working on it since late April and I could not have it finished in either May or June, which could have been fitting months 😅 but I’m glad to continue the series of these. This is the 8th iteration so far :)
